<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/css/bootstrap.min.css' %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all'%>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/js/bootstrap.min.js' %>
  </head>
  <body class="email">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <a href="http://manchestermakerspace.org/">
            <img src="https://makerspace-interface.herokuapp.com/assets/makerspace.png"
              alt="Manchester Makerspace"
              style="max-height: 116px;"/>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12">
              <h3>Welcome to Manchester Makerspace!</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12">
              <p>We're so glad you've decided to join us!</p>
              <a href="<%=%>">Click here to register for our Online Portal</a>

              <p>Please sign up for our Online Portal (above) where you can review our Member Contract, Code of Conduct, and pick an orientation time.  During orientation, we will get you setup with a keyfob for 24/7 member access and give you a brief tour of the premises to explain the procedures of the space and safety precautions.</p>

              <p>Additionally, our monthly equipment safety checkout day is the first Saturday of the month (except holidays). If there are any shops or equipment that you are particularly interested in, please let us know so the respective officers can plan accordingly</p>
              <p>Lastly, if you have any other questions, please reply to this email or email <a href="mailto:board@manchestermakerspace.org?subject=Re:%20Welcome%20to%20Manchester%20Makerspace" target="_top">board@manchestermakerspace.org</a>. Hope to see you at the space soon!</p>
              <br>
              <p>--The Manchester Makerspace Team</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
